---
// About Section Component
---

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="min-h-screen flex items-center py-24 bg-card relative">
	<!-- Subtle geometric background -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
		<div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-32 h-32 border border-emerald-300 dark:border-emerald-600 rotate-45"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-32 right-32 w-24 h-24 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 rotate-12"></div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
		<div class="text-center mb-20">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 via-red-600 to-blue-600 dark:from-orange-400 dark:via-red-400 dark:to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-8 tracking-tight">
				About
			</h2>
			<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 via-red-400 to-blue-400 dark:from-orange-500 dark:via-red-500 dark:to-blue-500 mx-auto mb-12 rounded-full"></div>
			<p class="text-xl text-foreground max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				<span class="text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Pulse COOP</span> is a worker-owned cooperative made up of creatives, musicians, and web technologists based in Austin. We believe in supporting local and small businesses, building tools for our community, and using technology to empower small organizations and grassroots movements.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<!-- What is a Co-op Section -->
		<div class="mb-16">
			<div class="group relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400/10 to-blue-400/10 dark:from-emerald-500/10 dark:to-blue-500/10 rounded-3xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
				<div class="relative bg-emerald-50/50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-emerald-200/50 dark:border-emerald-700/50 hover:border-emerald-300/50 dark:hover:border-emerald-600/50 transition-all duration-500">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-green-500 dark:from-emerald-400 dark:to-green-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6 text-center">What is a Co-op?</h3>
					
					<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Though we are a small team at the moment, we are constituted as a co-op, which means we operate as a <span class="text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 font-semibold">democratic workplace</span> and ascribe to the <span class="text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 font-semibold">seven cooperative principles</span>.
						</p>
						
						<p>
							Additionally, we donate labor to cooperatives and causes we feel passionate about.
						</p>
						
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-8">
							<a 
								href="https://www.ica.coop/en/cooperatives/cooperative-identity" 
								target="_blank" 
								rel="noopener noreferrer"
								class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-emerald-600 dark:bg-emerald-500 text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 dark:hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 text-sm"
							>
								<span class="mr-2">Learn about the Seven Principles</span>
								<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
								</svg>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
			<div class="group relative">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400/20 to-blue-400/20 dark:from-green-500/20 dark:to-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
				<div class="relative bg-card/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 rounded-3xl border border-green-200/50 dark:border-green-700/50 hover:border-blue-300/50 dark:hover:border-blue-600/50 transition-all duration-500">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-8">Our Values</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-6">
						<li class="group/item flex items-start">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 dark:bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mt-3 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-foreground text-lg">Worker Ownership</strong>
								<p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">Democratic decision-making and shared success</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="group/item flex items-start">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 dark:bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mt-3 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-foreground text-lg">Tech-Enabled Collaboration</strong>
								<p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">Building tools that bring communities together</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="group/item flex items-start">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 dark:bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mt-3 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-foreground text-lg">Local & Small Business Support</strong>
								<p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">Strengthening our community's economic foundation</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="group/item flex items-start">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 dark:bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mt-3 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-foreground text-lg">Community Empowerment</strong>
								<p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">Technology that serves grassroots movements</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="group/item flex items-start">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 dark:bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mt-3 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 group-hover/item:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-foreground text-lg">Sustainability & Ethics</strong>
								<p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1">Responsible practices for long-term impact</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="group relative">
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400/20 to-orange-400/20 dark:from-red-500/20 dark:to-orange-500/20 rounded-3xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
				<div class="relative bg-card/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 rounded-3xl border border-red-200/50 dark:border-red-700/50 hover:border-orange-300/50 dark:hover:border-orange-600/50 transition-all duration-500">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-8">Our Team</h3>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="group/item p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-red-50/70 dark:hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground text-lg mb-1">Aastha Kumari Karki</h4>
							<div class="w-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-transparent group-hover/item:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
						</div>
						<div class="group/item p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50/70 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground text-lg mb-1">Andrew Riefenstahl</h4>
							<div class="w-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-transparent group-hover/item:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
						</div>
						<div class="group/item p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50/70 dark:hover:bg-green-900/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground text-lg mb-1">Riley Sklar</h4>
							<div class="w-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-transparent group-hover/item:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-muted/50 rounded-2xl border border-border/50">
						<p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed italic">
							"We are musicians and collaborators deeply connected to Austin's creative and tech scenes. Full bios coming soon."
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section> 